text: Rose Hill is a city in Iowa in the United States. == Geography == Rose Hill is located at 41°19′17″N 92°27′47″W (41.321389, -92.462952). According to the United States Census Bureau, the city has a total area of 0.14 square miles (0.36 km2), all of it land. ==References== Category:Cities in Iowa
title: Rose Hill, Iowa
